home.title: Ikhaya
home.footer: Iwebhusayithi manje ihunyushwe futhi iyabonakala ngezilimi eziyi-100 +!
home.descriptionA: Unonjiniyela wesoftware egcwele isitaki & unjiniyela wewebhu nomlando obonisiwe wokuhola ngempumelelo amaphrojekthi we-minecraft wokuthuthukisa isipiliyoni somsebenzisi ekuphenduleni.JS kanye nokusebenzisa izindlela eziphephile zokusebenzisana kanye nokubambisana kwethimba elisebenzayo.
home.descriptionB: Ngokwengeziwe, nginguMdali oqukethwe geography onikeze ngempumelelo ama-algorithms amapulatifomu amaningi okuxhumana nabantu, okubandakanya i-Instagram, i-YouTube, neTiktok, ukuthola isisekelo somlandeli esihlonishwayo futhi esihehayo.

personal_summary.title: Isifinyezo somuntu siqu
personal_summary.text: Njengomthuthukisi we-software ogcwele wesitaki osuselwa ku-Orlando, FL, ngikhombisile ubuchwepheshe kubuchwepheshe obuhlukahlukene, kusukela ku-Java naku-C + + ukuphendula.js kanye ne-Node.js. Ngomlando wethrekhi yamaphrojekthi aholayo, kufaka phakathi ukuthuthukiswa kohlelo lokuguqulwa kweJava lwe-Minecraft kanye newebhusayithi enomvuzo yabashayeli bamaloli, ngibonise ubuholi kanye nokwenziwa okusha. Ukuzibophezela kwami ​​okuhle kubonakala emandleni ami ukuhambisa ukuphathwa kwamaphrojekthi, futhi ukuletha izixazululo ezisezingeni eliphakeme ezithuthukisa isipiliyoni somsebenzisi kanye nempumelelo yenhlangano.

entries.title: Ubunjiniyela Obugcwele Be-Stack
entries.text: Nginikeza izixazululo eziphelele kulo lonke ukuthuthukiswa kokuphela kwangaphambi kokuphela nangemuva, ngiqinisekisa ukuhlanganiswa komthungo kanye nokusebenza kuyo yonke i-software stack yonke.

entries.title: Ukuthuthukiswa kweWebhu
entries.text: Ngobuchwepheshe ku-HTML, CSS, kanye nohlaka lweJavaScript efana ne-Rect.js, ngiqamba amawebhusayithi abonakalayo futhi asebenziseka kalula ahambisana nokuhlangabezana nezidingo ezithile nezintandokazi zamakhasimende.

entries.title: Ukuthuthukiswa komdlalo
entries.text: Izilimi ezivumayo ezifana neJava ne-C ++, ngisebenza ngokukhethekile ekwakheni okuhlangenwe nakho kwemidlalo okugxilile, kusukela emcabangweni nasekwakhiweni kokusebenzisa kanye nokwenza kahle, ukuqinisekisa i-gameplay yokubandakanya nokusebenza okubushelelezi.

biblioteca.title: I-BIBLIOTECA JSON
biblioteca.text: Iphrojekthi yePython ehlelela ukuhunyushwa kwezilimi. Ivumela iphothifoliyo yami yewebhusayithi ukuthi ihunyushwe ezilimini ezingama-70 +, kufaka phakathi iSpanishi, isiFulentshi, isiShayina, isi-Arabhu, nabanye abaningi. Le projekthi isetshenziselwa ukudala iphothifoliyo yewebhusayithi yezilimi eziningi, ewusizo kakhulu ekufinyeleleni izilaleli ezibanzi. Ngale phrojekthi, ngaphezu kwama-99% omhlaba angafunda iphothifoliyo yami ngolimi olulundayo.

connect_four.title: Xhuma ezine
connect_four.text: Umndeni omkhulu wokuqaliswa okungaphezulu kuka-50 + kwe-Xhuma umdlalo ezine. Le phrojekthi ifaka ukwenziwa kwezilimi ezahlukahlukene ezingama-30 ezahlukahlukene, kufaka phakathi iJava, C ++, Python, JavaScript, nokuningi. Ngokwengeziwe, kuhlanganisa nezinhlaka ezahlukene ezingama-20 + noma ezinye izindlela, kufaka phakathi ama-Reccul.js, Ruby ku-Rail, asp.net, nokuningi.

interop.title: Iphrojekthi ye-Interop
interop.text: Iphrojekthi ephathelene nokusebenzisana kwamabhuku phakathi kwezilimi ezahlukahlukene zokuhlela. Njengamanje kufaka phakathi izilimi ezi-15 ezahlukahlukene zokuhlela kanye namaphethini wokubulawa okungu-18.

formatter.title: JSON & Yaml Auto Formatter
formatter.text: I-linter ne-autoformatter yamafayela we-JSON & Yaml. Le phrojekthi isetshenziselwa ukufometha amafayela we-JSON & Yaml, asiza kakhulu ekugcineni ikhodi ihlanzekile futhi ihlelekile. Yakhelwe nge-Go, ihlanganiswe nge-webas maphakathi, futhi ifakwe kwiphothifoliyo yami njengephrojekthi yewebhusayithi. Amafomethi amaningi okuzayo ngokuzayo.

minecraft_json_generator.title: I-Minecraft JSON generator
minecraft_json_generator.text: I-Lightweight JSON generator eyakhelwe ePython ukuthola izinsiza zeMinecraft namaphakethe wedatha. Le phrojekthi isetshenziselwa ukukhiqiza amafayela we-JSON ngama-mods we-minecraft, kufaka phakathi izinto zangokwezifiso, amabhlokhi kanye nezinhlaka. Iwusizo kakhulu hhayi ukudala ama-datapacks ngokwezifiso kuphela, kepha ama-mods kanye nesici sokushintshana ngegama le-mod.

educational_experience.title: Isipiliyoni Sami Semfundo
educational_experience.text: Kanye namaphrojekthi ami uqobo, nami ngithole amakhono amaningi avela kokuhlangenwe nakho kwezemfundo. Chofoza lapha ukubuka iphrofayili yami ye-LinkedIn ukuthola eminye imininingwane.

professional_experience.title: Isipiliyoni sami sobuchwepheshe
professional_experience.text: Eceleni kwamaphrojekthi ami uqobo, nami ngithole amakhono amaningi avela kokuhlangenwe nakho okuhle. Chofoza lapha ukubuka iphrofayili yami ye-LinkedIn ukuthola eminye imininingwane.

portfolio_website.title: Iwebhusayithi yePortick Goodwin Portfolio
portfolio_website.text: Le webhusayithi iyiwebhusayithi yami yephothifoliyo yomuntu siqu, eyakhelwe nge-erract.js. Le projekthi isetshenziselwa ukukhombisa amakhono ami namaphrojekthi ami, kanye nokuhlinzeka ngeplatifomu yabaqashi abangahle bangithinte. Le projekthi isetshenziselwa ukudala ubukhona be-inthanethi ochwepheshe.

lua_library.title: Umtapo Wezwe UPatrick's Lua
lua_library.text: Umtapo wolwazi owusizo wemibhalo ye-LUA ukuze ubhekisele emuva esikhathini esizayo. Lo mtapo wolwazi usetshenziselwa ukwenza ezenzakalelayo imisebenzi emibhalweni yeLua, engangena kahle imisebenzi yokusebenza, njengoba i-lua imvamisa lulimi olusheshayo lokubhala kunawo womabili uPython noRuby.

excel_scripts.title: Imibhalo ye-Microsoft's Excel Spreadsheet (VBA)
excel_scripts.text: Umtapo wolwazi owusizo we-VBA script ye-Microsoft Excel. Lo mtapo wolwazi usetshenziselwa ukwenza imisebenzi kuma-spreadsheet ama-Excel.

neovim_config.title: I-novick's neovim Config
neovim_config.text: Ukucushwa kwami ​​komuntu siqu ne-neovim. Le phrojekthi isetshenziselwa ukumisa i-neovim ukuthanda kwami, kufaka phakathi ama-keybindings ngokwezifiso, izingqikithi nama-plugins. Le projekthi isetshenziselwa ukwenza i-neovim isebenziseka kalula futhi isebenze kahle ukusetshenziswa kwami.

python_maps.title: I-Patrick's Map Generator
python_maps.text: I-United States County & State Map Generator, eyakhiwe ngePython isebenzisa imitapo yolwazi ye-geopanda kanye ne-matplotlib. Le projekthi isetshenziselwa ukukhiqiza amamephu e-United States, kufaka phakathi amamephu we-County ne-State. Le phrojekthi isetshenziselwa ukudala amamephu wangokwezifiso wokubuka idatha nokuhlaziywa.

powershell_library.title: I-Patrick's Powershell Library Library
powershell_library.text: Umtapo wezincwadi owusizo we-Powerhells scripty ukuze uthole inkomba esizayo. Iwusizo ngesici se-script sephrofayela se-

ruby_library.title: I-Patrick's ruby ​​scriptary Library
ruby_library.text: Umtapo wolwazi owusizo wemibhalo kaRuby ukuze uyibhekisele esikhathini esizayo. Iwusizo ku-ruby yesikhathi esizayo emibonweni yentuthuko yentuthuko kajantshi.

pdf_builder.title: Umakhi wamakhono we-PDF
pdf_builder.text: Umakhi we-PDF wangokwezifiso owakhiwe ngePython nge-PDFKIT ne-JINJA2 Extensions, eceleni kwe-HTML ne-JSON KOSON. Le phrojekthi isetshenziselwa ukukhiqiza amafayela we-PDF ohlwini lwamakhono namaphrojekthi. Le phrojekthi ingahle isetshenziselwe ukudala ukuqalisa kabusha kwe-PDF yangokwezifiso, okuwusizo kakhulu kwizicelo zomsebenzi.

rijandel_encryption.title: Iphrojekthi ye-Rijandel Encryption
rijandel_encryption.text: Umndeni wokuqaliswa okungu-10 + weRijandel Encryption algorithm ngo-128, 192, kanye nama-256 bits. Le phrojekthi isetshenziselwa ukukhombisa i-rijandel encryption algorithm ezilimini ezahlukene zokuhlela izilimi. Le projekthi isetshenziselwa ukudala umndeni wokwenziwa kwe-rijandel encryption algorithm.

suprememc.title: I-Supermemc Minecraft Mod
suprememc.text: I-mod ye-minecraft eyengeza amathuluzi wangokwezifiso, izembatho zempi, izixuku, amabhlogo, ubukhulu, kanye nezinye izici eziningi kulo mdlalo. Yakhelwe izinguqulo zeJava 8-17 ngo-Khetha izinguqulo ze-minecraft phakathi kuka-1.16 no-1.20.

tiger_programming_language.title: Ulimi lwezinhlelo ze-Tiger
tiger_programming_language.text: Ulimi olwenziwe ngokwezifiso lwakhiwe kuzo zombili i-go & Rust ukuze uvivinye ukwakheka kwe-Interpreter nokusebenza. Isetshenziswe kuwebhusayithi yephothifoliyo usebenzisa iWebhu SOLDER.

tiger_tailgating_pros.title: Iwebhusayithi yeTiger Tailgating Pros
tiger_tailgating_pros.text: Iwebhusayithi engikwakhile ngo-2024 ngeTiger Tailating Pros, inkampani ehambisanayo eClemson, SC. Yakhelwe nge-hampeli.js.

turing_machine.title: Iphrojekthi yomshini wokuThupha
turing_machine.text: Umndeni wokuqaliswa ngaphezulu kwama-30 + womshini wokuswayipha. Kusetshenziselwe ukukhombisa ukuphelela kokuphela kwezilimi ezahlukahlukene zokuhlela ukucwaninga, ikakhulukazi ulimi lwezinhlelo ze-Tiger.

contact.title: Thinta mina
contact.description: Ngiphendula ngokubuza kusuka ku-imeyili, imilayezo ye-linkedIn, nemiyalezo ye-Instagram. Nami ngizophinde ngibuye uma inombolo yami ihlinzekwa kabusha nge-resume noma ngenye indlela, yize ngincamela ukugcina inombolo yami yocingo iyimfihlo.

formatter.title: JSON & YAML formatter
formatter.description: I-JSON & Yaml formatter iyithuluzi elikuvumela ukuthi ufometha amafayela we-JSON nama-Yaml. Yakhiwa nge-Go futhi webASCY, futhi yakhelwe ukuthi isheshe futhi isebenze kahle. Ifomethi yakhelwe ukuba kube lula ukuyisebenzisa, ngesibonisi esilula esikuvumela ukuthi unamathisele kwikhodi yakho ye-JSON noma ye-Yaml bese uyifometha ngokuchofoza inkinobho.

tiger.description: Ulimi lwe-Tiger Programming ulimi lulimi lwezinhlelo ngokwezifiso olusungulwe kuzo zombili i-go & Rust ukuze uvivinye ukwakheka nokusebenza kwe-Interpreter.
